# 🇬🇧 Technical English for CS

## 🏛 Style Standards
- IEEE/ACM/Springer Diction.
- Formal & Objective Tone.

## 📐 Key Rules
- Precision > Generality.
- Hedge claims (may, suggest).
- Use active voice for contributions.

## 📖 Power Verbs
- Utilize, Leverage, Employ.
- Illustrate, Demonstrate.
- Mitigate, Facilitate, Outperform.
